author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be Instagram and Facebook suddenly banning their users for the most insane reasons. The reasons issued would have the police investigating you if you were a user and with this problem seemingly only getting worse over a month, many are asking just what's going on. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: So Instagram Is Banning Everyone...
